LicenseDefinitionCustomPermission (Devel.name: LicenseDefinitionCustomPermission (Developer Preview)
LicenseDefinitionCustomPermission (Devel.description: Represents a licensed custom permission that controls access to a license's features when included in a custom permission set license definition.

LicenseDefinitionId.description: ID of the custom permission set license definition that contains the licensed custom permission.

LicensedCustomPermissionId.description: ID of the licensed custom permission that you're including in the permission set license definition. On the CustomPermission object, the isLicensed field must equal true.
